<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password - GrocerEase</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #c82333);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .alert-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        }
        
        .btn-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #c82333);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220,53,69,0.3);
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(220,53,69,0.4);
        }
        
        .security-tips {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .security-tip {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .tip-icon {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        
        .link-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üõí GrocerEase</div>
            <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
            <p>üîí Secure your account</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h3>Hello <%= name %>!</h3>
            
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your GrocerEase account. If you made this request, click the button below to reset your password:</p>
            
            <div class="btn-container">
                <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="btn">Reset My Password</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> This password reset link will expire in <strong><%= expiryHours || 24 %> hours</strong> for your security.
            </div>
            
            <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <div class="link-box"><%= resetLink %></div>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <h4>üõ°Ô∏è Security Tips for a Strong Password:</h4>
                
                <div class="security-tip">
                    <span class="tip-icon">‚úì</span>
                    <span>Use at least 8 characters with a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="security-tip">
                    <span class="tip-icon">‚úì</span>
                    <span>Avoid using personal information like birthdays or names</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="security-tip">
                    <span class="tip-icon">‚úì</span>
                    <span>Don't reuse passwords from other accounts</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="security-tip">
                    <span class="tip-icon">‚úì</span>
                    <span>Consider using a password manager</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #f8d7da; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong>üö® Didn't request this?</strong><br>
                If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately. Your account is safe.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Need help?</strong> Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@grocerease.com" style="color: #dc3545;">support@grocerease.com</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d;">
                ¬© 2025 GrocerEase. All rights reserved.<br>
                This email was sent to <%= email %>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
